      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NICMAC ACE (8) has a strong record this trip including two wins from four starts. Comes off a (24.49) win last time, scoring by 2.75 lengths in a T3 Grade 7 over 425m at Bendigo. Looks suited here and rates on top. CHIC IN PARIS (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (26.02) in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win at this track. The form from her last run stacks up well. Key runner on best form. VESTA BALE (1) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at Ballarat over 450m behind Yondu Bale (26.30) in a T3 RSTW. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from six starts. Has ability and can measure up. PRICKLE (7) looks a chance coming off a month layoff.",
